        "payload": "{\"external\":{\"rows\":[\"Pharos Main\",\"Pharos 2\",\"Pharos 3\",\"Cinema Dome Brightsign\",\"Cinema LED columns\",\"Water Feature 1\",\"Water Feature 2\",\"Water Feature 3\"],\"cols\":[\"Status / Mode\",\"Now Playing\"],\"values\":{\"Pharos Main\":{\"Status / Mode\":\"Online · Enabled\",\"Now Playing\":\"Show 1\"},\"Pharos 2\":{\"Status / Mode\":\"Online · Enabled\",\"Now Playing\":\"Ambiance 1\"},\"Pharos 3\":{\"Status / Mode\":\"Offline\",\"Now Playing\":\"—\"},\"Cinema Dome Brightsign\":{\"Status / Mode\":\"Online · Enabled\",\"Now Playing\":\"Show 1\"},\"Cinema LED columns\":{\"Status / Mode\":\"Online · Manual Override\",\"Now Playing\":\"Loop: Promo A\"},\"Water Feature 1\":{\"Status / Mode\":\"Online · Enabled\",\"Now Playing\":\"Ambiance 2\"},\"Water Feature 2\":{\"Status / Mode\":\"Fault (E‑Stop)\",\"Now Playing\":\"Stopped\"},\"Water Feature 3\":{\"Status / Mode\":\"Online · Enabled\",\"Now Playing\":\"Scheduled\"}}}}",
